at_bat.description: Ben Revere doubles to deep right center field.
Mike Trout called out on strikes.
Albert Pujols homers to left field. Ben Revere scores.
Kole Calhoun homers to center field.
Andrelton Simmons grounds out to shortstop, Tim Beckham to Trey Mancini.
Luis Valbuena lines out to shallow center field to Manny Machado.
Tim Beckham pops out to shallow right field to Kaleb Cowart.
Manny Machado grounds out to second base, Kaleb Cowart to C.J. Cron.
Jonathan Schoop grounds out to shortstop, Andrelton Simmons to C.J. Cron.
C.J. Cron homers to center field.
Martin Maldonado lines out to left field to Craig Gentry.
Kaleb Cowart homers to center field.
Ben Revere flies out to left field to Craig Gentry.
Mike Trout lines out to right field to Anthony Santander.
Adam Jones pops out to shallow infield to C.J. Cron.
Trey Mancini grounds out to third base, Luis Valbuena to C.J. Cron.
Mark Trumbo homers to left field.
Anthony Santander pops out to shallow center field to Kaleb Cowart.
Albert Pujols lines out to second base to Trey Mancini.
Kole Calhoun strikes out swinging.
Andrelton Simmons grounds out to second base, Jonathan Schoop to Trey Mancini.
